javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget, javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class IslandSubScene extends javafx.scene.layout.AnchorPane implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
class IslandSubScene is used for represent the single islands with the addition of students, towers and mother nature on them during the game
